title: Australian diary. No. 069
creator_credit: Australian National Film Board and Jack S. Allan
brief_description: The following items are featured in this interesting cinemagazine: fine wine production is shown in the Hunter Valley; shellfish, pippies are becoming a popular sea-food; Scottish cattle, Aberdeen Angus are thriving on a property called Belltrees and a story on Meteor men. members of the RAAF in Korea.
